@startuml
!include _style.puml

title AI Quant 安全视图（Security View）

rectangle "浏览器" as browser <<UI>> #ECFDF5
rectangle "Web 前端\n:5173" as web <<UI>> #ECFDF5
rectangle "Backend API\n:8000" as api <<API>> #EFF6FF
rectangle "Streamlit\n:8501" as st <<UI>> #ECFDF5

database "MySQL\nhuahua_trade" as mysql <<DB>> #EFF6FF
cloud "QMT Gateway（外部）" as qmt <<SEC>> #FEE2E2
cloud "LLM/Embedding（外部）" as llm <<SEC>> #FEE2E2
cloud "Web Search（外部）" as search <<SEC>> #FEE2E2
folder ".ai_quant（本地）" as rt <<RUNTIME>> #FFF7ED

browser --> web : HTTPS（生产建议）
web --> api : REST /api/*\nCORS 受控
st --> api : REST /api/agent/run

api --> mysql : DB 凭证（环境变量）
api --> qmt : X-API-Token\n(AI_QUANT_QMT_GATEWAY_TOKEN)
api --> llm : DASHSCOPE_API_KEY
api --> search : TAVILY_API_KEY（规划/可选）
api --> rt : 落盘日志/产物/索引

note right of api
现状：无统一登录态/JWT\n建议：生产加 API Key/JWT + RBAC\n并限制暴露的路由与 CORS
end note

note bottom of rt
`.ai_quant` 含日志与研报产物\n可能包含敏感信息（prompt/数据片段）\n应纳入访问控制与备份策略
end note

@enduml
